1
00:00:04,909 --> 00:00:07,749
But anything
and all things are possible

2
00:00:07,749 --> 00:00:11,965
in the Absolute,
and the Absolute’s devotees

3
00:00:11,965 --> 00:00:15,068
who control the Absolute,

4
00:00:15,068 --> 00:00:17,065
if that’s possible.

5
00:00:17,065 --> 00:00:18,774
And apparently it is.

6
00:00:18,774 --> 00:00:20,178
[How to Control the Absolute]

7
00:00:20,178 --> 00:00:22,319
Śrī Kṛṣṇākarṣiṇī cha sā (Brs: 1.1.17).

8
00:00:22,319 --> 00:00:27,937
The Absolute
Independent Supreme Reality,

9
00:00:27,937 --> 00:00:30,788
the Original Source of everything,

10
00:00:30,788 --> 00:00:35,647
for Whom not a blade of grass
moves without His will;

11
00:00:35,647 --> 00:00:39,081
the Supreme Omniscient
Omnipotent Lord,

12
00:00:39,081 --> 00:00:43,085
Personality of Godhead, 
Svayam Bhagavān,

13
00:00:44,390 --> 00:00:47,052
can be controlled

14
00:00:47,052 --> 00:00:48,675
through love and devotion.

